                    </label>
                </div>
            </form>
            <br />
            <p class="intro">Checkboxes can be displayed with a simple label for basic checkboxes. If the users attention should be drawn to the checkbox, a styled title can be added to the label using a <code>span</code> tag.</p>
        </div>
        <h2>Radio Buttons</h2>
